"title": "4438: eating",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4438",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The consumption of food, necessary for survival. Scripture cites enjoyment of eating as a gift of God but emphasises that it is not the main priority in life, for God will provide abundantly for his children.</p>\n<h2>Eating for survival</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:1-Neh5:2\">NEH 5:1–5:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:20-Gen28:22\">GEN 28:20–28:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:12\">1KI 17:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:3-1Kgs19:8\">1KI 19:3–19:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:3\">2KI 25:3</a></p>\n<h2>Eating as a sign of life and health</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:28\">DEU 4:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:5-2Sam13:10\">2SA 13:5–13:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:4\">PSA 102:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:35-Mark5:43\">MRK 5:35–5:43</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:49-Luke8:56\">LUK 8:49–8:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:36-Luke24:43\">LUK 24:36–24:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:48-John6:58\">JHN 6:48–6:58</a></p>\n<h2>Enjoyment of eating as a gift of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:13\">ECC 3:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:1-Gen27:25\">GEN 27:1–27:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:24-Eccl2:25\">ECC 2:24–2:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:18\">ECC 5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:15\">ECC 8:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:7\">ECC 9:7</a></p>\n<h2>God blesses his people with sufficient food</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:25\">PSA 37:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:3-Lev26:5\">LEV 26:3–26:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:23-Lev26:26\">LEV 26:23–26:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:16\">DEU 8:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:15\">DEU 11:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:7\">DEU 12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:11-Josh24:13\">JOS 24:11–24:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:26\">PSA 22:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:23-Ps78:29\">PSA 78:23–78:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:2\">PSA 127:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps128:1-Ps128:2\">PSA 128:1–128:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:25\">PRO 13:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:19\">ISA 1:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:22\">ISA 7:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:13\">ISA 65:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:21-Isa65:22\">ISA 65:21–65:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:26\">JOL 2:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:14\">AMO 9:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:9-Mic6:16\">MIC 6:9–6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:5-Hag1:11\">HAG 1:5–1:11</a></p>\n<h2>Eating should not be one's chief priority</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:1-Matt4:4\">MAT 4:1–4:4</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:1-Luke4:4\">LUK 4:1–4:4</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:3\">DEU 8:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:4-Num11:34\">NUM 11:4–11:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:25-Matt6:34\">MAT 6:25–6:34</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:22-Luke12:31\">LUK 12:22–12:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:16-Luke12:20\">LUK 12:16–12:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:13-Col2:17\">COL 2:13–2:17</a></p>\n<h2>Eating as a religious observance</h2>\n<h3>Sacrificial meals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:12\">EXO 18:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:32-Exod29:33\">EXO 29:32–29:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:6\">EXO 32:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:14-Lev7:10\">LEV 6:14–7:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:31\">LEV 8:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:21-Lev21:23\">LEV 21:21–21:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:8-Num18:13\">NUM 18:8–18:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut15:19-Deut15:20\">DEU 15:19–15:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:1-1Sam1:5\">1SA 1:1–1:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam9:11-1Sam9:13\">1SA 9:11–9:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:24-1Sam20:29\">1SA 20:24–20:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:3\">EZK 44:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos8:13\">HOS 8:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:9-Heb13:10\">HEB 13:9–13:10</a></p>\n<h3>Sacrificial meals for pagan gods</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:15\">EXO 34:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:5-Ezek18:6\">EZK 18:5–18:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:14-Ezek18:15\">EZK 18:14–18:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:9\">EZK 22:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:4-1Cor8:13\">1CO 8:4–8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:23-1Cor10:28\">1CO 10:23–10:28</a></p>\n<h3>The Passover and Feast of Unleavened Bread</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:1-Exod12:11\">EXO 12:1–12:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:14-Exod12:20\">EXO 12:14–12:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:4-Lev23:8\">LEV 23:4–23:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:16-Num28:25\">NUM 28:16–28:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:1-Deut16:8\">DEU 16:1–16:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:17-Matt26:19\">MAT 26:17–26:19</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:12-Mark14:16\">MRK 14:12–14:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:7-Luke22:13\">LUK 22:7–22:13</a></p>\n<h3>The Lord's Supper</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:26-Matt26:29\">MAT 26:26–26:29</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:22-Mark14:25\">MRK 14:22–14:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:17-Luke22:20\">LUK 22:17–22:20</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:23-1Cor11:34\">1CO 11:23–11:34</a></p>\n<h2>Restrictions on eating</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:1-Gen9:4\">GEN 9:1–9:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:15-Gen2:17\">GEN 2:15–2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:1-Gen3:7\">GEN 3:1–3:7</a> <em>Eve and Adam eat the fruit of the tree</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:22\">GEN 3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:22-Gen32:32\">GEN 32:22–32:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:32\">GEN 43:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:31\">EXO 22:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev7:19\">LEV 7:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev7:22-Lev7:27\">LEV 7:22–7:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:1-Lev11:47\">LEV 11:1–11:47</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:3-Deut14:20\">DEU 14:3–14:20</a> <em>clean and unclean food</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:4-Lev22:8\">LEV 22:4–22:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:6\">LEV 23:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:1-Num6:4\">NUM 6:1–6:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:23-Deut12:25\">DEU 12:23–12:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:31\">EZK 44:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:14-Mark7:19\">MRK 7:14–7:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:1-Rom14:3\">ROM 14:1–14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:19-Rom14:21\">ROM 14:19–14:21</a></p>\n<h2>Eating and hospitality</h2>\n<h3>Eating at a royal court</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:7\">1KI 2:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam9:1-2Sam9:13\">2SA 9:1–9:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:19\">1KI 18:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:26\">DAN 11:26</a></p>\n<h3>Eating as a guest in another's home</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:3-Gen18:5\">GEN 18:3–18:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:3\">GEN 19:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:16\">GEN 43:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:18-Exod2:20\">EXO 2:18–2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg19:5-Judg19:9\">JDG 19:5–19:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:8\">2KI 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:6-Prov23:7\">PRO 23:6–23:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:9-Matt9:13\">MAT 9:9–9:13</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:14-Mark2:17\">MRK 2:14–2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:27-Luke5:32\">LUK 5:27–5:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:6-Matt26:7\">MAT 26:6–26:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:3\">MRK 14:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:1-Luke14:14\">LUK 14:1–14:14</a></p>\n<h2>Fasting</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth4:16\">EST 4:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam3:35\">2SA 3:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:1-Matt4:2\">MAT 4:1–4:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:1-Luke4:2\">LUK 4:1–4:2</a></p>\n<h2>Cannibalism</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:53\">DEU 28:53</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:24-2Kgs6:29\">2KI 6:24–6:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer19:9\">JER 19:9</a></p>\n<h2>Metaphorical references to eating</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:50\">JHN 6:50</a></strong> <em>Coming to faith in Jesus Christ</em>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:20\">REV 3:20</a></strong> <em>Having fellowship with Jesus Christ.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps14:4\">PSA 14:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps53:4\">PSA 53:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps141:4\">PSA 141:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:29-Prov1:31\">PRO 1:29–1:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:17\">PRO 4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:21\">PRO 18:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:27\">PRO 31:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:1\">SNG 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:1-Isa55:2\">ISA 55:1–55:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:1-Ezek3:3\">EZK 3:1–3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:1-Mic3:3\">MIC 3:1–3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:7\">REV 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev10:9\">REV 10:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:16\">REV 17:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:17-Rev19:19\">REV 19:17–19:19</a></p>",
